snippet.title: Smash Ultimate Stage Mod - Poké Floats (Melee)
snippet.description:
Download: https://gamebanana.com/mods/479066
Stage mod for Super Smash Bros. Ultimate.
Poké Floats from Melee makes a comeback, goes over Saffron City.
Another port from a past Smash game, and this is one of the most popular stages from the entire series, i'm really happy i managed to do this.
This was a pretty exausting stage to do, i took a break from it for some days after making the collisions.
Hope you guys like it.

It's not perfect at the moment, but i'm happy with how it is right now, though i do plan on fixing some stuff soon
